rded in [chat history](history-and-feedback.md) entries (except in [private mode](../chats.md#private-mode)).\n-   The book editor accepts drag-and-drop uploads through the same upload endpoint (e.g. for `KNOWLEDGE` files); the [PWA share target](../ui/embedding-and-pwa.md#share-target) stores shared files the same way.\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null,"userModified":false}}
